dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Mount Baldy quadrangle, Los Angeles and San Bernardino counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from newest available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle MOUNT BALDY, CA 1972, NIMA 2452 IV SE - Series V895."
"Prepared in cooperation with the Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History and the Angeles National Forest."
Includes col. cross section, quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
